  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个APB总线监控模块的架构图，核心功能是捕获APB信号并生成监控数据包。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "apb_monitor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，这个监控模块主要处理APB协议的哪些信号？是标准的APB3还是APB4信号集？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "apb_monitor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "按APB3标准来，需要包含psel、penable、pwrite、paddr、pwdata、prdata、pready和pslverr这八个信号。我们把它们归到一个叫APB Signals的分组里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB_Signals",
        "psel",
        "penable",
        "pwrite",
        "paddr",
        "pwdata",
        "prdata",
        "pready",
        "pslverr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经创建了APB Signals分组，把这八个信号都放进去了。接下来监控模块内部怎么划分功能块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB_Signals",
        "psel",
        "penable",
        "pwrite",
        "paddr",
        "pwdata",
        "prdata",
        "pready",
        "pslverr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "监控模块内部需要三层：第一层是信号捕获Capture，在psel和penable同时为高时的posedge采样；第二层是事务跟踪Trans，识别传输的起止；第三层是报告器Reporter，负责打包输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "apb_monitor",
        "Capture",
        "Trans",
        "Reporter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "三层结构清晰，Capture负责采样，Trans跟踪状态，Reporter生成数据包。我注意到Capture的触发条件是psel & penable，这个采样时机会不会漏掉setup phase的数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Capture",
        "psel",
        "penable"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "不会，APB的setup phase只有psel为高而penable为低，真正有效的数据在access phase两者都为高时锁存，所以posedge采样psel & penable能抓到稳定的数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Capture",
        "psel",
        "penable"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，我在Capture节点里标注了\"Sample @ posedge when psel & penable\"。Trans层的起止条件怎么定义？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Capture",
        "Trans"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "事务开始条件是psel为高且penable为低，表示进入setup phase；结束条件是pready有效或者pslverr报错，这两个信号任一拉高就表示传输完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans",
        "psel",
        "penable",
        "pready",
        "pslverr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加，Trans节点标注为\"Start: psel & !penable End: pready | pslverr\"。Reporter层输出什么样的数据包？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans",
        "Reporter",
        "psel",
        "penable",
        "pready",
        "pslverr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Reporter要生成包含命令、数据和性能信息的packet，我们叫PKT节点，输出到监控总线。另外需要一个独立的Output分组来展示最终的监控总线接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reporter",
        "PKT",
        "Output",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以Reporter内部的PKT生成cmd/data/perf三类信息，然后通过MONBUS输出。这个MONBUS是64位宽吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reporter",
        "PKT",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，MONBUS是64位监控总线，信号命名用mon_*前缀。Output分组就叫Monitor Bus Output，里面放MONBUS节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Output",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构都搭建好了，现在需要连接数据流。八个APB信号都连到Capture，这个我理解。Capture到Trans、Trans到Reporter、Reporter到MONBUS的流向对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB_Signals",
        "Capture",
        "Trans",
        "Reporter",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流向正确。Capture采样后的数据送给Trans做事务识别，Trans把完整的transaction信息给Reporter打包，最后Reporter输出到MONBUS。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Capture",
        "Trans",
        "Reporter",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "所有连接都画好了。我检查一下分组命名：APB_Signals、apb_monitor、Capture、Trans、Reporter、Output，层级关系都正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB_Signals",
        "apb_monitor",
        "Capture",
        "Trans",
        "Reporter",
        "Output"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Capture、Trans、Reporter这三个应该是apb_monitor的子分组，不是独立节点。另外APB_Signals的分组标题用英文双引号标注清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "apb_monitor",
        "Capture",
        "Trans",
        "Reporter",
        "APB_Signals"
