      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "只在posedge采样，但采样条件必须同时满足psel和penable为高。这个设计是为了对齐APB的时钟域，避免亚稳态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Capture",
        "psel",
        "penable"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Capture节点的描述保持\"Sample @ posedge when psel & penable\"。Trans层的结束条件里pready和pslverr是或关系，这个优先级有讲究吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Trans",
        "pready",
        "pslverr"
